Key Match Events: The Houston Rockets won against the Memphis Grizzlies with a score of 128-108.
Jalen Green led the scoring for the Rockets with 22 points.
Alperen Sengun and Jabari Smith Jr. dominated the rebounding with 15 and 16 rebounds respectively.
The Rockets grabbed a total of 64 rebounds, including 23 offensive boards.
Houston scored 39 points in the third quarter and 30 points in the fourth quarter.
